# idle-react lint

After changing any file under `idle-react/`, run lint from that package before finishing:

```bash
cd idle-react && npm run lint
```

Fix all reported errors and warnings in the files you touched (or related fixes if the change surfaced new issues). Do not leave the package in a failing lint state.
